        Built with absolute privacy by <a href="https://caiatech.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Caiatech</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="privacy-guarantee">
        <strong>Privacy Guarantee:</strong> No cookies ‚Ä¢ No analytics ‚Ä¢ No third-party scripts ‚Ä¢ No cloud processing ‚Ä¢ No data storage
      </p>
      <p class="links">
